EHEAL

   By means of this spell, low to mid ranked Lunar Magi
   are able to call upon the Green moon for solace. The
   Lunar Mage will heal at a highly accelerated rate, 
   but this is truly expensive and taxing in energy. Once
   the healing has started, the mage may use 'endheal'
   to halt it at anytime.  The spell automatically ends
   if the caster has no more energy.

 GL: 5  COST: 25 + average 10 per interval
